How to translate difficult words from 

While +v1+ing
koi kam karte karte

sote-sote->while sleeping
padhte-padhte->while reading

he spealks while sleeping.
he was crying while reading.
the penny scratched while scratching.
the pot fell while falling.


After+v1+ing
1.Nhakar->After bathing
2.Khakar->after eating
3.Sokar-<After sleeping

i will come after bathing.
he was sleeping after eating.
  
